      "text": "凄い……トリエルも、リズノワも\nお姉ちゃんの曲を完璧に歌ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing… TRINITYAiLE and LizNoir.\nThey’re singing Mana’s songs perfectly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2,
      "endTime": 17.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
