      "text": "練習の合間によく踊ってるって聞いてたけど\nまさかグループ用にアレンジまでしてるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard they practiced her songs in between their usual practice.\nBut to think they’d even make dance arrangements for themselves…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.433333333333334,
      "endTime": 24.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
