      "text": "星見プロの内輪ライブなのがもったいないくらいね……\nって、あら？　人が集まってきてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like too much for just an in-house Hoshimi Productions show…\nWhat’s this? A crowd is gathering?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 32.88742837451753,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
