      "text": "さっき何してるのか聞かれたから、麻奈ちゃんの\nバースデーライブの準備だよーって言っちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone asked earlier what we were doing‚ and I let slip\nthat we were preparing for Mana-chan’s birthday live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 42.99999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
